== Other ==
* {{ill|Tenshinyama (Rakugo)|ja|天神山 (落語)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshinyama (Rakugo)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - A performance of {{ill|Kamigata Rakugo|ja|上方落語|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamigata Rakugo|1=Kamigata rakugo|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q524880}}. The story is set in {{ill|Tennoji Ward, Osaka|ja|大阪市天王寺区|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennoji Ward, Osaka|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} near {{ill|Yasui Shrine|ja|安居神社|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Shrine|1=Yasui Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11450228}} on the uplands of {{ill|Uemachi Plateau|en|Uemachi Plateau|WD=Q7877450|lt=Uemachi Plateau|1=Uemachi Plateau}}, historically referred to as Tenshinyama.
